## Project Structure

```
project-root/
├─ src/                     # Source code
│  ├─ [module-name]/        # Feature modules
│  │  ├─ models.py          # Data models
│  │  ├─ services.py        # Business logic
│  │  ├─ views.py           # API endpoints/controllers
│  │  └─ tests/             # Unit tests
│  ├─ common/               # Shared utilities
│  └─ config/               # Configuration
├─ tests/                   # Integration/E2E tests
├─ docs/                    # Documentation
├─ scripts/                 # Build/deploy scripts
└─ [config files]           # package.json, requirements.txt, etc.
```

**Key directories:**
- `src/[module]/models/` - Data models and database schemas
- `src/[module]/services/` - Business logic (follows service pattern)
- `src/[module]/views/` - API endpoints or UI controllers
- `tests/` - Test files mirror src/ structure

